# Keep the build context to runtime code only. Excluding test data and LFS-
# tracked fixtures stops the image from shipping LFS pointer files / CV samples.
.git/
.github/
.worktrees/
tests/
tasks/
reports/
scripts/
assets/
docs/

__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.venv/
venv/

*.md
!README.md
# Runtime guard: src/gander/prompts/*.md are loaded at request time, not docs.
# Today's `*.md` is anchored and does NOT cross `/`, so it already leaves the
# nested prompts in the context (verified by building and listing them). This
# explicit re-include documents that they are load-bearing and keeps them in
# the image even if a broader rule (e.g. `**/*.md`) is added here later.
!src/gander/prompts/*.md
.env
.env.*
